* Wed Sep 20 2017 Liz Nemsick <lnemsick.simp@gmail.com> - 7.0.1-0
- Add libxkbcommon-x11 to required package list for CentOS/RedHat 7.4.
- Remove unnecessary CentOS data-in-module files.  The OS family fact
